#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""24HG Proton/Wine Version Selector — Smart Proton management for gaming

Commands:
    check <game>           Check best Proton version for a game
    apply <game> [version] Set Proton version for a game (or auto-pick best)
    list                   List all installed Proton versions
    install <version>      Install a Proton version (GE, official, TKG)
    remove <version>       Remove a Proton version
    test <game>            Quick-test a game with different Proton versions
    report <game>          Submit compatibility report to Hub
    update                 Check for Proton-GE updates
    auto on|off            Auto-pick Proton version when launching games
    tricks <game>          Apply common Winetricks for a game
"""

